WEBVTT

00:00.868 --> 00:02.401
<i>NARRATOR: Previously on Hostages.</i>

00:02.403 --> 00:04.570
This is Vanessa Moore. My sister.

00:04.572 --> 00:06.606
You are a beautiful woman.

00:06.608 --> 00:10.042
<i>KRAMER: This guy came at us.
He pulled a gun. I killed him.</i>

00:10.044 --> 00:12.111
- Kramer Delaney?
- Why do you wanna talk to me?

00:12.113 --> 00:14.780
I can explain downtown.

00:14.782 --> 00:17.516
I'd like you to meet Special
Agent Carlisle with the FBI.

00:17.518 --> 00:19.552
He's helping us in our
investigation into the

00:19.554 --> 00:21.354
disappearance of your friend, Angela.

00:21.356 --> 00:23.522
So what do you think?
She telling the truth?

00:23.524 --> 00:26.625
My gut tells me she's credible.

00:26.627 --> 00:28.460
There's just no way out of this.

00:28.462 --> 00:31.363
- Unless...
- Unless what?

00:31.365 --> 00:32.798
We kill him.

00:32.800 --> 00:34.532
What about the poison he gave you?

00:34.534 --> 00:36.701
We just need some professional help here.

00:36.703 --> 00:39.537
I don't have a lot of
killers on my speed dial. You?

00:39.539 --> 00:41.206
I might know someone who does.

00:41.208 --> 00:43.441
- Ellen?
- I need help.

00:43.443 --> 00:45.810
Of course. Tell me everything.

00:48.781 --> 00:50.715
- Who is this?
- We have a lot to discuss.

00:52.285 --> 00:54.152
Killing Duncan is a terrible mistake.

00:54.154 --> 00:56.788
The second he's dead, my
partners will cut their losses

00:56.790 --> 00:59.123
and slaughter each and every one of us.

00:59.125 --> 01:00.424
<i>Brian, it's me.</i>

01:00.426 --> 01:01.625
Just... I'll explain everything later,

01:01.627 --> 01:02.994
but call me back, as soon as you can, okay?

01:05.129 --> 01:06.097
Nice job.

01:13.906 --> 01:15.006
No, no, no, no, no!

01:20.645 --> 01:21.745
Stop!

01:24.382 --> 01:26.116
(GRUNTING)

01:26.118 --> 01:27.284
(DUNCAN GROANING)

01:32.427 --> 01:33.513
We need him alive.

01:35.918 --> 01:36.836
Don't move. Don't, don't.

01:36.837 --> 01:38.590
We need to minimize the poison
spreading through your body.

01:38.594 --> 01:39.894
Let me do it.

01:39.896 --> 01:41.962
I spoke to Burton, I get
it. If you die, we die.

01:49.604 --> 01:52.806
What the hell are you doing?
This is our chance, just kill him!

01:52.808 --> 01:55.342
Just do it, just get it over with!

01:55.344 --> 01:58.044
- Just do it!
- We can't. I'll explain later.

01:58.046 --> 02:00.013
Please just get my medical
bag, I need a scalpel.

02:00.015 --> 02:01.648
Why the hell are you doing this?

02:01.650 --> 02:03.383
This is the poison you gave
me to use on the President.

02:03.385 --> 02:05.686
- Some of it went in. I need to know what it is.
- It's a paralytic.

02:05.688 --> 02:09.521
It's fast acting. I'll lose muscle
function, the ability to breathe, speak.

02:12.092 --> 02:15.261
I'm not dead yet, you move an inch
and I'll put you down for good.

02:15.263 --> 02:17.396
- Drop it.
- ELLEN: How much time do we have?

02:17.398 --> 02:19.199
- A few minutes.
- I need to cut it out.

02:19.201 --> 02:20.900
There's a knife in my hip, use it.

02:23.937 --> 02:25.270
(GROANING)

02:25.272 --> 02:26.672
This is gonna hurt.

02:26.674 --> 02:30.376
Ellen, just kill him. Do this,
and we get our lives back.

02:30.378 --> 02:32.311
Everything just goes away.

02:35.081 --> 02:36.081
Ah.

02:38.385 --> 02:39.751
We need ice.

02:39.753 --> 02:42.321
Brian, like it or not, our
lives depend on his right now.

02:42.323 --> 02:43.753
There are other people behind this,

02:43.754 --> 02:45.512
and if he dies, they will come for us.

02:45.559 --> 02:46.992
You need to trust me.

02:52.765 --> 02:54.967
Stay with me, Duncan. Stay with me.

